description:
Chris Hemsworth is an actor, producer and host known for his movies like Thor and Extraction, as well as his documentary show Limitless. His new movie Crime 101 is in theaters now. 

Chris joins Theo to talk about his childhood in Australia, connecting with his dad through his battle with Alzheimers, and what hes learned about longevity after putting his own body to the test.
